  %% HackTrap AI Threat Monitor - Component Diagram

  subgraph Client
    UI[index.html and styles.css]
    State[main.js state and render pipeline]
    Map[Leaflet map]
    SocketClient[Socket IO client]
    RestClient[REST fetch client]
  end

  subgraph API
    Server[server.js HTTP and WebSocket]
    Generator[generator.js synthetic events]
    Analyzer[analyzer.js threat and prediction]
    Profiles[profiles.js attacker profiles]
    Memory[In memory event and profile state]
  end

  UI --> State
  State --> Map
  State --> SocketClient
  State --> RestClient

  SocketClient <-->|WebSocket: new_event| Server
  RestClient <-->|REST: /api/events| Server
  RestClient <-->|REST: /api/system-status| Server
  RestClient <-->|REST: /api/attackers| Server
  RestClient <-->|REST: /api/attackers/:ip| Server

  Server --> Generator
  Generator --> Analyzer
  Analyzer --> Profiles

  Generator --> Memory
  Analyzer --> Memory
  Profiles --> Memory
  Server --> Memory
